text: LA-11 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Chaudhary Muhammad Yaseen of PPP. It covers the area of Charhoi Tehsil in Kotli District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
